@node "Copyright" "Copyright"
 The Bootmonitor is freeware, that means, it`s allowed to copy free it but you
must not change the Bootmonitor for commercial purposes or pass on it not
entirely. But you can include into this packet new icons. The original icons
have to end on .original then, not on .image.

The @{"VersionĀ1.3" link "Version13" 0} of the BootMonitor is GIFTWARE !!

The @{"VersionĀ1.4" link "Version14" 0} of the BootMonitor is Shareware and @{"canĀbeĀupdated" link "Version15" 0}.

The @{"VersionĀ1.5" link "Version15" 0} of the BootMonitor is Shareware and @{"canĀbeĀupdated" link "Version16" 0}.

The @{"VersionĀ1.6" link "Version16" 0} of the BootMonitor is Shareware and @{"canĀbeĀupdated" link "Version17" 0}.

The @{"VersionĀ1.7" link "Version17" 0} of the BootMonitor is Shareware (@{"turnĀtoĀFuture" link "Future" 0}) !!
@endnode

