in this version I include 4 printer routines and the menues, which need the
asl.library, give you, if you don`t have this library, a message, that they
are no available.

The menu are the same like in the previous version, and you can read
informations at @{"VersionĀ1.3" link "Version13" 0}.

The new items on menu are:

 @{"PrintĀDatei" link "FPrint" 0}
 @{"DumpĀDatei" link "FDump" 0}
 @{"PrintĀBB" link "Print" 0}
 @{"DumpĀBB" link "Dump" 0}

BootMonitor V1.4 is now Shareware !! In the limited version you can use the
new items once, and if use it twice, a shareware-message appears. If you want
the full-version, contact follow @{"Adress" link "Adresse" 0}. Either you send me the registration
formular and the shareware fee and receive a disc with the full-version or you
